TitleEnglish: Miniforce: Deeno the King of Dinosaurs
SummaryEnglish: Curious boy 'Yan' meets 'Dino' with the key to the king of dinosaurs and becomes a secret friend. Meanwhile, the space villain 'Queen' threatens the earth, and the 'Mini Commando' has an all-time showdown with the king of dinosaurs 'Dino'...!
